[The EIA case in the town of Contes, Alpes-Maritime, reportedly related to the current case in Lorgues, was reported on Fri 29 Dec 2017 as an immediate notification to the OIE; see 20180103.5534216. The said post includes Mod.CRD's background information on EIA, to which interested subscribers are referred. - Mod.AS

